# Create Release
git checkout main
git pull origin main  # 确保主分支是最新的
git checkout -b release/v1.0.0

# version.py
__version__ = "1.0.0"

# Release Notes for Version 1.0.0

## New Features
- Added functionality to add and manage books.

## Bug Fixes
- Fixed issue with adding books without title or author.

git add version.py RELEASE_NOTES.md
git commit -m "Prepare for release v1.0.0"

git checkout main

git merge release/v1.0.0
